lead_paragraph: Gusting winds created second-round havoc at Augusta National  but could not blow Jordan Spieth from the top of the Masters leaderboard on Friday while helping lift Rory McIlroy's career grand slam bid.

headline.print_headline: Spieth Hangs On as Winds Create Masters Havoc
